Package it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable

Class Mapped

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable.Deliverable
      • it.polimi.ingsw.network.common.deliverable.Mapped
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Mapped
extends Deliverable
    Mapped-type Deliverables are sent by the Server to query the Client about multiple-choice questions. The server is blocked waiting until a Response is sent back by the client.
    See Also:
